---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Legal Information</h1>

<section class="mb-8">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Privacy Policy</h2>
  <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
    <p class="mb-4">
      This website respects your privacy by default. Browsing is anonymous and doesn't require any form of registration.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1">
      <li><strong>Cookie-free</strong>: No tracking or profiling cookies are used.</li>
      <li><strong>Privacy-First Analytics</strong>: I use a self-hosted, privacy-focused analytics solution. Data is collected in a fully anonymized form for statistical purposes only (e.g., page views) without storing IP addresses or personal information.</li>
      <li><strong>No Third Parties</strong>: Your browsing data is never sold, shared, or shared with third-party advertisers.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mb-8">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Terms & License</h2>
  <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
    <p class="mb-4">
      The source code of this portfolio is released under the <strong>MIT License</strong>. You are free to fork it and use it as a template for your own work.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4 border-l-2 border-primary pl-4 italic">
      <strong>Note</strong>: While the codebase is open-source, the personal content—including my biography, project descriptions, and personal images—remain the intellectual property of <strong>Lorenzo Della Mea</strong> and may not be used for commercial purposes or redistributed as your own without explicit permission.
    </p>
    <p>
      All materials are provided "as is", without warranty of any kind.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="pt-8 text-sm text-gray-500 text-center">
  © {year} Lorenzo Della Mea. Built with Astro.
</footer>
